'''Khilese''' was the native language of the [[Khil]] species from [[Belnar/Legends|Belnar]]. Most Khils were fluent in both Khilese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]]. Khils produced their own languages using the strands of flesh clanging from their faces, or [[hullepi]], drawing air around and through hullepi of different thickness or length. The result was a melodious language that other species find melodious, but none can reproduce. Communication was only but one of the different uses of the hullepi. Khilese had a [[Written Khilese|written form]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

